The future of home technology has arrived, control your ROBOTIKA smart connected devices remotely, whether you are at home or out and about.
Set automations, timers and more to control and customise your Robotika product experience!

(1) Download our ROBOTIKA app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our ROBOTIKA app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Search ROBOTIKA skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(4) Enable ROBOTIKA skill, and you'll be navigated to ROBOTIKA login page;
(5) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(6) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on robot”
“Alexa, turn off robot”
“Alexa, start robot”
“Alexa, set robot to dock”
